---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Free Resume Builder" description="ResumeBuilder privacy policy. Learn how we handle your data and protect your privacy.">
  <section class="hero-split" style="padding-bottom:0;min-height:auto">
    <div class="hero-split-content" style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding:0">
      <span class="eyebrow">Privacy</span>
      <h1>Our <span class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</span></h1>
      <p>Last updated: June 1, 2026</p>
      <div class="hero-split-actions" style="justify-content:center">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Build My Resume</a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">View Examples</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <article>
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to ResumeBuilder. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information when you use our resume building service.</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>When you use our resume builder, you may provide us with personal information including your name, email address, phone number, work history, education details, and other information typically found on a resume. This data is processed entirely in your browser and is not stored on our servers.</p>

        <h3>2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p>We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our website. This collects anonymous data such as: pages visited, time spent on site, browser type, and general location (country/city level). We do not collect any personally identifiable information through analytics.</p>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To provide and maintain our resume building service</li>
          <li>To improve our website based on usage patterns</li>
          <li>To respond to your inquiries when you contact us</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>Your resume data is stored locally in your browser's localStorage. We do not transmit, store, or have access to the resume content you create. We implement appropriate security measures to protect any information we do collect.</p>

        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use minimal cookies required for Google Analytics functionality. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings. No tracking cookies are used for advertising purposes.</p>

        <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use Google Analytics for website analytics. Google's privacy policy can be found at https://policies.google.com/privacy. We do not share your personal data with any other third parties.</p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to: access any personal data we hold about you, request deletion of your data, opt-out of analytics tracking, and export your resume data at any time. Since we store minimal data, most of these rights are automatically fulfilled by the client-side nature of our service.</p>

        <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at privacy@resumebuilder.com.</p>

        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the new policy on this page with an updated date.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-sm section-tools">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Free Career Tools</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Resume Builder</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/ats-score" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>ATS Score</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/cover-letter" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Cover Letter</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Examples</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/templates" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Templates</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 17H20"/><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 014 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 2z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Blog</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="capture">
    <div class="capture-inner">
      <h3>Get Weekly Resume Tips</h3>
      <p>Join 10,000+ job seekers getting expert advice straight to their inbox.</p>
      <form class="capture-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();var e=this.querySelector('input');if(e.value){alert('Thanks for subscribing!');e.value=''}">
        <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
      <p class="capture-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
